# Aevus SCADA Intelligence Platform

AI-powered SCADA monitoring for midstream oil & gas infrastructure.

**Status:** Pre-revenue testbed
**Stack:** Python/FastAPI + InfluxDB + WebSocket
**Infra:** AWS EC2 (t3.small) + WireGuard VPN to lab hardware
